Variables :
Variables are creating a memory and storing data in the background
Storing and working with data in computer's memory

type(variable) function ---> will tell us what datatype the variable contains
id(variable) function   ---> will tell us the memory in which the variable is stored

1) Variable can start with any alphabet ie ---> A-->Z or a ---> z
2) variable should not start wih digit.
3) variable should not be keyword
4) variable should not start with special characters ie !,@,#,$,
5) variable,method or function starting with underscore ie (_) then it is considered as private variable
